          "content": "## Operations Management Overview\nOperations Management (OM) deals with designing, managing, and improving production and service processes.\n\n### Transformation Process\nInputs → Processes → Outputs\n\n### Types of Operations\n- Manufacturing\n- Service\n\n### Importance\n- Improves efficiency\n- Reduces costs\n- Enhances quality\n\n### Example\nA factory converting raw materials into finished goods.",
